          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " is the web browser of choice here at BestTechie. Vivaldi is fast, secure, easy to use, and works great. It's also based on Chromium, the browser developed by Google and used to build Google Chrome which gives Vivaldi a lot of great features right out of the box.",
